Veusz basic installation procedure
----------------------------------

As the code is so immature, I do not include instructions on how to
install this program in its own directory, just run it.

Requirements:
 python 2.2.3    http://www.python.org/
 PyQt            http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/pyqt/
 Numarray        http://www.stsci.edu/resources/software_hardware/numarray

(PyQt requres
 QT              http://www.trolltech.com/products/qt/ )

Install the above requirements.

To test the plotting functionality, run

python tests/testgraph.py

or test the primative user interface, run

./veusz.py

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
